'''葛倫·愛德華·葛林華德'''（{{lang-en|Glenn Edward Greenwald}}，{{bd|1967年|3月6日}}），美國[[律師|律師]]、[[新聞從業員|新聞從業人員]]與作家。2012年8月至2013年10月間，曾任《{{tsl|en|Guardian US|美國衛報}}》（''Guardian US''）專欄作家<ref name="Carr2012" /><ref name="Salon071912" /><ref name="GreenGuard" />。2007年至2012年間，也曾為[[Salon.com|Salon.com]]寫過專欄，並為英國《[[衛報|衛報]]》供稿<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/dec/14/bradley-manning-deserves-a-medal |location=London |work=The Guardian |first=Glenn |last=Greenwald |title=Bradley Manning deserves a medal |date=2011-12-14 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2013-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130712074531/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/dec/14/bradley-manning-deserves-a-medal |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/cifamerica/2011/jul/21/barack-obama-social-security-cuts |location=London |work=The Guardian |first=Glenn |last=Greenwald |title=Barack Obama is gutting the core principles of the Democratic party |date=2011-07-21 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2013-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130204042207/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/cifamerica/2011/jul/21/barack-obama-social-security-cuts |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/cifamerica/2011/oct/07/cia-impunity-torture-tapes |location=London |work=The Guardian |first=Glenn |last=Greenwald |title=The CIA's impunity on 'torture tapes' |date=2011-10-07 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2013-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313040231/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/cifamerica/2011/oct/07/cia-impunity-torture-tapes |dead-url=no }}</ref>。葛林華德亦曾任[[宪法|宪法]]與[[公民权利和政治权利|公民权利和政治权利]]律師。在《Salon》網站上，葛林華德身兼專欄作家與部落客，關注政治與法律議題<ref name=SalonProfile />。他亦為包含《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》<ref name="NYT20090428"/><!-- <ref name="NYT20090223"/><ref name="NYT20090317"/> -->、《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》<ref name=LaTimes />、《{{tsl|en|The American Conservative|美國保守派}}》雜誌<ref name=TAC>{{cite web |title=Author Search: Glenn Greenwald |url=http://www.amconmag.com/search.html?v&m=3&author=Glenn+Greenwald&start=0&end=25 |work=[[The_American_Conservative|The American Conservative]] |accessdate=2008-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090120215734/http://www.amconmag.com/search.html?v&m=3&author=Glenn+Greenwald&start=0&end=25 |archive-date=2009-01-20 |dead-url=yes }} When "Glenn Greenwald" is provided as a search term selecting the "author" field: (1) "Madness of Crowds"; (2) "Selective Amnesia"; (3) "Watching the Detectives"; and (4) "Authoritarian Temptation."</ref>、《[[國家利益_(雜誌)|國家利益]]》雜誌<ref name=NIO>{{cite web |first=Glenn |last=Greenwald |title=The Perilous Punditocracy |url=http://www.nationalinterest.org/Article.aspx?id=17444 |work=[[The_National_Interest|The National Interest]] |publisher=[[The_Nixon_Center|The Nixon Center]] |date=2008-04-25 |accessdate=2008-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210150825/http://www.nationalinterest.org/Article.aspx?id=17444 |archive-date=2008-12-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，與《{{tsl|en|In These Times|當今時代}}》雜誌<ref name=ITT>{{cite web |first=Glenn |last=Greenwald |title=Author Profile:Glenn Greenwald |url=http://www.inthesetimes.com/community/profile/3753 |work=[[In_These_Times|In These Times]] |date=2006-07-21 |accessdate=2008-12-14 |archive-date=2015-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930071756/http://inthesetimes.com/community/profile/3753 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Rechecking>{{cite journal |first=Glenn |last=Greenwald |title=Rechecking the Balance of Powers |url=http://www.inthesetimes.com/article/2730/rechecking_the_balance_of_powers |journal=[[In_These_Times|In These Times]] |volume=30 |issue=8 |date=2006-07-21 |accessdate=2008-12-14 |archive-date=2009-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090213113146/http://www.inthesetimes.com/article/2730/rechecking_the_balance_of_powers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在內的其他報紙或政治新聞雜誌供稿。2014年2月，他與{{tsl|en|Laura Poitras|罗拉·柏翠丝}}、{{tsl|en|Jeremy Scahill|杰里米·斯卡希尔|-{zh-cn:杰里米·斯卡希尔;zh-tw:傑瑞米·史卡希爾;zh-hk:謝洛美·史卡希}-}}一同成為《[[The_Intercept|The Intercept]]》共同編輯<ref name=TI>{{cite web |url=https://firstlook.org/theintercept/staff/ |title=Staff – The Intercept |accessdate=2014-01-08 |archive-date=2015-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813182606/https://firstlook.org/theintercept/staff/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

葛林華德被《[[外交政策_(杂志)|外交政策]]》雜誌選為「2013年全球百大思想家」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/2013_global_thinkers/public/greenwald |title=The Leading Global Thinkers of 2013 |publisher=Foreign Policy |date= |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108140903/http://www.foreignpolicy.com/2013_global_thinkers/public/greenwald |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的五本著作中，有四本曾被列入[[紐約時報暢銷書榜|《紐約時報》暢銷書排行榜]]。葛林華德亦是校園演說家，足跡遍布[[哈佛法学院|哈佛法学院]]、[[耶鲁法学院|耶鲁法学院]]、[[宾夕法尼亚大学|賓州大學]]、[[布朗大学|布朗大学]]、[[加州大学洛杉矶分校法学院|加州大学洛杉矶分校法学院]]、[[威斯康星大学麦迪逊分校|威斯康星大学麦迪逊分校]]與[[馬里蘭大學學院市分校|馬里蘭大學學院市分校]]。葛林華德也是廣播與電視節目常客。

葛林華德2009年時曾獲{{tsl|en|Izzy Award|依奇獎}}獨立新聞獎<ref name="Ithaca Award">{{cite web |url=http://www.ithaca.edu/news/release.php?id=2646 |title=Glenn Greenwald And Amy Goodman Share Inaugural Izzy Award For Independent Media |work=Ithaca News Release |publisher=[[Ithaca_College|Ithaca College]] |date=2009-03-05 |accessdate=2009-03-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305151154/http://www.ithaca.edu/news/release.php?id=2646 |archivedate=2009-03-05 }}</ref>，2010年時曾獲{{tsl|en|Online News Association|線上新聞協會|線上新聞協會獎}}最佳評論獎<ref name="OJA Award">{{cite web |url=http://conference.journalists.org/2010conference/2010/10/30/online-journalism-awards-honor-the-best-of-the-best |title=Online Journalism Awards, 2010 |publisher=[[Online_Journalism_Awards|Online Journalism Awards]] |date=2010-10-31 |accessdate=2010-10-31 |archive-date=2010-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101101163416/http://conference.journalists.org/2010conference/2010/10/30/online-journalism-awards-honor-the-best-of-the-best/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 早期生活與求學歷程 ==
葛倫·葛林華德出生在[[紐約|紐約]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1985-03-13/news/8501090703_1_greenwald-council-member-condos|work=Sun Sentinel|first=Gary|last=Stein|title=At 18, Future Holds Promise|date=1985-03-13|accessdate=2019-08-19|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194619/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1985-03-13/news/8501090703_1_greenwald-council-member-condos|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。葛林華德家庭在葛倫還是嬰兒時搬去了[[劳德代尔湖_(佛罗里达州)|勞德代爾湖，佛羅里達州]]<ref name="SalonProfile" /><ref name="GreenwaldResponse"/><ref name="Buzzfeed" />。葛倫的父母是[[猶太人|猶太人]]，他們和葛倫的祖父母曾嘗試讓他加入[[猶太教|猶太教]]，但他並沒有加入任何宗教組織，也沒有接受[[猶太教成人禮|猶太教成人禮]]。葛倫表示他的道德規範不會以宗教教義的方式呈現<ref name="mxPKN" />。 他在1990年獲得[[喬治華盛頓大學|喬治華盛頓大學]]哲學學士學位並在1994年獲[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]法學院法學博士學位<ref name="SalonProfile" /><ref name="Buzzfeed" />。

== 近況 ==
2013年6月，葛林華德因透過《衛報》刊登了詳述美國與英國{{tsl|en|Global surveillance|全球監測}}計畫，並由[[爱德华·斯诺登|-{zh-cn:爱德华·斯诺登;zh-hk:愛德華·斯諾登;zh-mo:愛德華·斯諾登;zh-tw:愛德華·史諾登;}-]]揭露機密文件的系列報導而聲名遠播<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/07/glenn-greenwald-edward-snowden-documents_n_3716424.html?utm_hp_ref=media |work=[[Huffington_Post|Huffington Post]] |last=Boadle |first=Anthony |title=Glenn Greenwald: Snowden Gave Me 15-20,000 Classified Documents |date=August 6, 2013 |accessdate=August 9, 2013 |archive-date=2017-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129153519/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/07/glenn-greenwald-edward-snowden-documents_n_3716424.html?utm_hp_ref=media |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/aug/18/david-miranda-detained-uk-nsa |location=London |work=The Guardian |first=Glenn |last=Greenwald |title=Glenn Greenwald: detaining my partner was a failed attempt at intimidation |date=2013-08-19 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506171144/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/aug/18/david-miranda-detained-uk-nsa |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這系列葛林華德與其他人合作出版的報導，讓他獲頒[[普利策奖|普利策奖]]{{tsl|en|Pulitzer Prize for Public Service|普立茲獎公共服務獎|公共服務獎}}<ref>Fung, Catherine, [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/20/glenn-greenwald-pulitzer-reliable-sources_n_5182297.html Glenn Greenwald Reacts To Pulitzer Prize] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/20/glenn-greenwald-pulitzer-reliable-sources_n_5182297.html |date=20170316221051 }}, ''Huffington Post'', April 20, 2014</ref><ref name="pulitzer prize">{{cite press release |url=http://www.theguardian.com/media/2014/apr/14/guardian-washington-post-pulitzer-nsa-revelations |title=Guardian and Washington Post win Pulitzer prize for NSA revelations |date=2014-04-14 |access-date=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506164448/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2014/apr/14/guardian-washington-post-pulitzer-nsa-revelations |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

葛林華德針對[[美国国家安全局|美国国家安全局]]（NSA）的報導，讓他在全世界獲得無數獎項，包含{{tsl|en|George Polk Awads|乔治·波尔克奖|-{zh-hans:乔治·波尔克奖;zh-tw:喬治·潑克獎;zh-hk:佐治·伯格獎}-}}{{tsl|en|George Polk Awards|國家安全報導獎}}、2013年線上新聞獎<ref>{{cite news |author=Martin Pengelly in New York |url=http://www.theguardian.com/media/2013/oct/20/guardian-nsa-files-online-journalism-awards |title=Guardian wins two online journalism awards for NSA Files reporting |publisher=theguardian.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308185350/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2013/oct/20/guardian-nsa-files-online-journalism-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並以在巴西《{{tsl|en|O Globo}}》雜誌接露NSA亦針對巴西人民進行監控的報導，獲得{{tsl|en|Esso Journalism Award|艾索新聞獎|-{zh-hant:艾索新聞獎;zh-hans:埃索新闻奖;}-}}（是第一個獲得此獎的外國人士）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.premioesso.com.br/site/noticias/release_2013_04.aspx |title=PrÃªmio Esso de Jornalismo 2013 |publisher=Premioesso.com.br |date= |accessdate=2014-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620055819/http://www.premioesso.com.br/site/noticias/release_2013_04.aspx |archivedate=2014-06-20 }}</ref>，此外還有阿根廷《{{tsl|en|Perfil}}》雜誌2013年的國際言論自由獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.perfil.com/sociedad/Premios-Perfil-a-la-Libertad-de-Expresion-y-la-Inteligencia-2013-20131106-0038.html |title=Premios Perfil a la Libertad de Expresión y la Inteligencia 2013 |publisher=Perfil.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-date=2014-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003193717/http://www.perfil.com/sociedad/Premios-Perfil-a-la-Libertad-de-Expresion-y-la-Inteligencia-2013-20131106-0038.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及[[电子前哨基金会|电子前哨基金会]]2013年的先鋒獎<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.eff.org/awards/pioneer/2013 |title=EFF Pioneer Awards 2013 |publisher=Electronic Frontier Foundation |date=2013-09-19 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627032826/https://www.eff.org/awards/pioneer/2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

葛林華德揭露NSA文件的過程，被拍成電影《[[第四公民|第四公民]]》，並一舉獲得2014年[[奥斯卡最佳纪录片奖|奥斯卡最佳纪录片奖]]。葛林華德在頒獎典禮上與本片導演罗拉·柏翠丝一同現身領獎<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.newyorker.com/news/amy-davidson/is-citizenfour-worth-celebrating |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124070814/https://www.newyorker.com/news/amy-davidson/is-citizenfour-worth-celebrating |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

葛林華德現與其伴侶大衛·迈克尔·密蘭達同住於他的故鄉[[巴西|巴西]][[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]<ref name=GreenwaldResponse /><ref name="Out.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.out.com/news-commentary/2011/04/18/glenn-greenwald-life-beyond-borders?page=0,0 |title=Glenn Greenwald: Life Beyond Borders |publisher=Out.com |date=2011-04-18 |accessdate=2012-12-09 |archive-date=2013-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629024717/http://www.out.com/news-commentary/2011/04/18/glenn-greenwald-life-beyond-borders?page=0,0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.listener.co.nz/culture/books/glenn-greenwald-interview |title=Glenn Greenwald interview |work=[[New_Zealand_Listener|New Zealand Listener]] |date=2012-02-04 |accessdate=2012-12-09 |archive-date=2012-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120811000236/http://www.listener.co.nz/culture/books/glenn-greenwald-interview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Silverstein>{{cite news |first=Ken |last=Silverstein |url=http://www.harpers.org/archive/2008/02/hbc-90002466 |title=Six Questions for Glenn Greenwald on Campaign Coverage |work=[[Harper's_Magazine|Harper's Magazine]] |date=2008-02-21 |accessdate=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2009-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090105102304/http://www.harpers.org/archive/2008/02/hbc-90002466 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=GreenwaldAOTPInt>{{cite web |author=Art of The Possible |url=http://www.theartofthepossible.net/2008/05/05/glenn-greenwald-an-interview-with-the-art-of-the-possible |title=Interview with Glenn Greenwald |work=Art of the Possible Blog |date=2006-01-16 |accessdate=2008-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080508160950/http://www.theartofthepossible.net/2008/05/05/glenn-greenwald-an-interview-with-the-art-of-the-possible/ |archive-date=2008-05-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。葛林華德表示，自己會選擇住在巴西，是因為美國的[[捍卫婚姻法案|捍卫婚姻法案]]拒絕承認同性婚姻，導致其伴侶無法獲得在美國與他共同居住的簽證<ref name="Out.com" />。葛林華德亦擔心若返回美國境內，會遭到逮捕<ref name="Ratner">{{cite news |url=http://therealnews.com/t2/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=31&Itemid=74&jumival=11896 |work=The Real News Network |first=Michael |last=Ratner |title=Twitter Storm between WikiLeaks and Glenn Greenwald |date=2014-11-04 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2017-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119045911/http://therealnews.com/t2/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=31&Itemid=74&jumival=11896 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2020年10月29日，葛林華德表示由於《The Intercept》拒絕刊登他批評美國民主黨總統候選人[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]的文章，他已辭去在《The Intercept》的職位<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/contenu/20201030-%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E6%8B%92%E5%88%8A%E6%89%B9%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0-%E6%99%AE%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%B9%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%BB%E8%91%9B%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%8E%E5%BE%B7%E6%84%A4%E8%80%8C%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C |title=媒体拒刊批拜登文章 普立兹得主葛林华德愤而离职 |website=法廣 |date=2020-10-30}}</ref>。

